1.) Who led this raid?<br>
It was lead by Divinus Veritas, and thus the rules on looting items are set up by them.<br>
<br>
2.) Were outsiders invited or did they ask to join?<br>
They asked if they could join in on the kill, and Divinus Veritas glady accepted the help.<br>
