4.) Were the looting rules stated before the raid?<br>
Yes, and it was clearly said that this ranger would be allowed to loot. If you had questions or concerns on who this ranger was all you had to do is ask, or type /who &lt;Ranger's Name&gt;. Then you would have easily found out what lvl he was and voice your opinion. Phoenixx would have explaned the situation, and then you could have made the choice if you wanted to stay or not. If you stay you still get your fair chance on the loot, and if you leave you have to wait for the next spawn.<br>
