5.) Did everyone get a fair shot at the loot?<br>
Yes, everyone was given a fair shot on each item droped, and the ranger in question only lottoed for one of the characters that were there. Phoenixx could have been unfair and let both characters lotto, but he didn't. Therefore, everyone got the same chance at winning an item.<br>
